0Z","msg":"明明班人篇講稿都係你比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924207e2e585293e80b6d7ffd4dd2d9bd377dd07","tid":2147770,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"消滅奶共狗"},{"pid":"1326e4b3a6a0ba84b8b80b13a29008e2cf98e205","tid":2147770,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:33:42.000Z","msg":": GOOD DOG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e86730a734108cda86af2946fa6f4124ce264be","tid":2147770,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cdd9fd7d5036ba966a3b25deddac9ab31cf4dc","tid":2147770,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"話雖如此，但很抱歉我是一頭港豬，愛國悟性不足，有個問題很想跟駱主任探討：既然制裁原是光榮，那「港區國安法」何故禁止愛國市民遊說外國政府制裁中共官員呢？眾所週知，中共鷹犬從不畏美國惡勢力，對於制裁，只會像林鄭所說，「一笑置之嗤之以鼻」；現在駱主任又公開對香港人說，原來美國制裁證明他們做了該做的事，那麼廣大愛國市民，呼籲美帝繼續給官員頒發「愛國愛港認證」，激勵他們做更多應該做的事，不是很合情合理嗎？合情合理的事，怎麼會不合法呢？懇請駱主任慶祝完畢後，可撥冗賜教！<br />\n<br />\n梁振英，加油！ - 馮睎乾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2147436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2147436</a>"},{"pid":"43a9a1b3b393e265fbc3a77e563911b21247f531","tid":2147770,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"通常得把口嘅人都係冇料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cd50642bd4d693cddd0b52b57db35ad3fef6d9","tid":2147770,"uid":288393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"有力反制呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeec6c111c20839a9af1d993a734cd95bc7b0acc","tid":2147770,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:52:02.000Z","msg":"鄭若華為國捐軀 無撚左幾廿億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6288318a361481f599d47cd40b576adc4c2fc7b9","tid":2147770,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"點呀，無反制就收皮啦"},{"pid":"302de64a0fcceae6b4bc9049ed01df8b0b557462","tid":2147770,"uid":224801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"自打嘴巴，又話制裁無用，依家又話穩定軍心，無用架話洗咩穩定軍心"},{"pid":"113c91ca4ff82c1ffa029ba9ea2c8e768fae2dea","tid":2147770,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"光榮都有兩種，一是為國捐軀的光榮，另外一種是揚威地球的光榮，例如拿諾貝爾獎。"}]}